                </div>

                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="JavaScript API" class="scroll-mt-20">
                    JavaScript Scope API
                </RzHeading>
                <RzParagraph>
                    The provider exposes these properties and methods to the Alpine scope (e.g., via <code>x-on:click</code>).
                </RzParagraph>
                <div class="not-prose mt-6 mb-10 overflow-hidden rounded-md border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800">
                    <table class="w-full text-sm">
                        <thead class="text-left bg-zinc-100/75 font-semibold text-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900/50 dark:text-zinc-300">
                            <tr>
                                <th scope="col" class="p-4 w-1/4">Name</th>
                                <th scope="col" class="p-4">Description</th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody class="divide-y divide-zinc-200 dark:divide-zinc-800">
                            <tr>
                                <td class="p-4 font-mono text-sky-600">date</td>
                                <td class="p-4 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">Get/Set the selected date string (YYYY-MM-DD).</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="p-4 font-mono text-sky-600">formattedDate</td>
                                <td class="p-4 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">Read-only localized string of the selected date.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="p-4 font-mono text-sky-600">dates</td>
                                <td class="p-4 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">Raw array of selected date strings.</td>
                            </tr>
                             <tr>
                                <td class="p-4 font-mono text-sky-600">setToday()</td>
                                <td class="p-4 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">Sets the selection to the current date.</td>
                            </tr>
                             <tr>
                                <td class="p-4 font-mono text-sky-600">addDays(n)</td>
                                <td class="p-4 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">Adds <code>n</code> days to the current selection.</td>
                            </tr>
                             <tr>
                                <td class="p-4 font-mono text-sky-600">clear()</td>
                                <td class="p-4 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">Clears all selected dates.</td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </section>

        </MainContent>
    </RzArticle>
</RzQuickReferenceContainer>

